# Change Log
All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

## [2.0.0] - 14-09-2018

### Added
- Add Nginx with PHP 7.2 configuration
- Add a Slim PHP 7.2 configuration without the web server

### Changed
- Add new tags with dedicated folders
- Improve directory structure overall

## [1.1.0] - 05-08-2017

### Changed
- Update composer.json file dependencies
- Update default bash aliases
- Update Dockerfile base image to PHP 7.1
- Update README

### Removed
- Remove Database container dependency from scripts

## [1.0.0] - 08-05-2017

### Added
- Add Dockerfile
- Add Apache `.htaccess`
- Add basic script for configuration